                        28</ref>)</center> </sourceNote></section><section id="ID_1438410834130_084" name="s1...2" temporalId="sch1_P2_s1...2" class="no_header"><num value="1...2"><inline class="not_bold">1-2.</inline></num><sourceNote>(Repealed <ref href="/hk/2011/17">17 of 2011 s.
